Once we went to a hotel in India.

00:40:32.166 --> 00:40:34.417
So we had some American friends

00:40:34.999 --> 00:40:38.166
and as usual, I mean, you can't eat like Americans can,

00:40:38.166 --> 00:40:40.542
you know. Is, Indians can't compete.

