Can eat a lot.

00:40:43.083 --> 00:40:45.250
So they were eating, eating, eating and,

00:40:45.500 --> 00:40:47.834
but we couldn't cope with them, really, to be very frank,

00:40:47.834 --> 00:40:49.625
I mean, we're no good.

00:40:49.959 --> 00:40:54.750
After some time they said, "Have you finished?" I said, "Yes."

00:40:55.041 --> 00:40:56.875
"All right..." they called the waiter,

00:40:56.875 --> 00:40:59.166
"Pack this out." I said, "What?

