Want to pack this for what?" "We paid for it."

00:41:02.750 --> 00:41:06.709
"So you paid for it, but I mean...In India nobody will eat a food

00:41:06.999 --> 00:41:08.709
which somebody else has eaten."

00:41:08.959 --> 00:41:10.375
"No, you pack it."

00:41:10.625 --> 00:41:12.542
And they had no shame about it;

00:41:12.834 --> 00:41:14.999
so shameless. I said.

00:41:14.999 --> 00:41:16.750
"We don't do this in India."

00:41:16.750 --> 00:41:18.875
Said, "Why not?" I said,. "These are bad manners."

00:41:18.875 --> 00:41:20.417
"But we've paid for it.

00:41:20.709 --> 00:41:23.291
Once you've paid for it then there is no bad manners."

00:41:25.250 --> 00:41:27.417
I said, "Ah, we don't want this to pack."

00:41:27.417 --> 00:41:29.417
"We'll have it. We'll have it in the night.

00:41:29.417 --> 00:41:31.166
We'll have it in the evening."

00:41:31.166 --> 00:41:34.500
I was surprised that such miserly people

00:41:34.500 --> 00:41:36.542
are saying that they are very rich

00:41:36.542 --> 00:41:39.875
and they think no end of themselves; extremely miserly.

