00:42:05.166 --> 00:42:09.959
Why? Because the whole thing is, 'we paid for it'.

00:42:11.250 --> 00:42:14.875
I mean you go to any place,

00:42:14.875 --> 00:42:18.542
any restaurant there or anything, you'll be amazed.

00:42:19.417 --> 00:42:21.375
They pack things for you

00:42:21.625 --> 00:42:23.709
if something is left over in America.

