Now how you must communicate

00:49:46.667 --> 00:49:48.834
decently,

00:49:49.250 --> 00:49:50.834
with very tender

00:49:52.834 --> 00:49:57.125
and very beautiful mannerism

00:49:57.458 --> 00:50:01.333
you have to talk to another person,

00:50:01.792 --> 00:50:04.083
talk to other Sahaja Yogis,

00:50:04.542 --> 00:50:06.250
talk to anyone,

00:50:07.000 --> 00:50:09.917
is in a very sweet manner you should talk.

00:50:09.917 --> 00:50:13.166
I do not mean the French style, you see,

00:50:13.166 --> 00:50:17.291
bending your body and all artificial stuff. Not that.

00:50:17.291 --> 00:50:22.375
I'm saying that if you are naturally talking to somebody,

00:50:23.625 --> 00:50:26.375
you should talk with decent language,

00:50:27.750 --> 00:50:31.500
with decency, with humility

00:50:32.917 --> 00:50:35.041
and need not go on jabbering all the time

00:50:35.041 --> 00:50:37.625
and talking too much. There's no need.

00:50:38.375 --> 00:50:40.250
But, on the contrary,

00:50:40.583 --> 00:50:42.959
this was the style was Shri Krishna.

00:50:43.166 --> 00:50:46.125
In short, His power was madhurya;

00:50:46.583 --> 00:50:49.500
is the sweetness, like the honey.

00:50:51.291 --> 00:50:54.959
When you are worshiping Shri Krishna

00:50:55.166 --> 00:50:57.834
you have to know that you must talk

00:50:58.166 --> 00:51:02.875
in a manner that will please another person.

00:51:20.041 --> 00:51:23.709
So, while talking to anyone

00:51:23.709 --> 00:51:26.125
you can talk very sweetly,

00:51:26.583 --> 00:51:31.625
very nicely and in a way which will please that person,

00:51:31.625 --> 00:51:33.125
not to provoke,

00:51:33.125 --> 00:51:35.709
not to say things which are hard.

00:51:36.166 --> 00:51:38.166
But some people have a habit

00:51:38.583 --> 00:51:43.250
of saying all the time something which is very provoking,

00:51:44.000 --> 00:51:46.583
which is not at all good.

00:51:47.834 --> 00:51:50.583
But some people are,

00:51:52.458 --> 00:51:56.166
when it comes to their business are very sweet,

00:51:57.125 --> 00:52:00.709
but when it comes to something else they are very harsh.

00:52:01.041 --> 00:52:03.750
We have a Jain community in India.

00:52:04.125 --> 00:52:05.750
I've seen many Jains.

00:52:06.250 --> 00:52:08.375
When they are for their business

00:52:08.625 --> 00:52:10.625
they're the sweetest you could know,

00:52:11.333 --> 00:52:16.959
but when it comes to something else

00:52:17.250 --> 00:52:20.125
like donating some money or something,

00:52:20.625 --> 00:52:22.959
they're extremely hard.

00:52:23.458 --> 00:52:26.125
They will only donate for stupid things,

00:52:26.500 --> 00:52:29.166
but not for something sensible.

00:52:29.917 --> 00:52:32.709
They'll work for something extremely stupid,

00:52:33.250 --> 00:52:35.834
but never for anything sensible.

00:52:35.834 --> 00:52:39.458
We have another community called as Sindhis.

00:52:39.458 --> 00:52:42.166
I think they are under the influence of the West.

00:52:42.542 --> 00:52:44.917
Same with the Western people.

00:52:45.542 --> 00:52:48.999
If you show that you have some business with them,

00:52:49.999 --> 00:52:52.166
suddenly you know, they change.

00:52:52.542 --> 00:52:54.875
Suddenly they change. You can't understand

00:52:55.083 --> 00:52:57.041
what has happened to this man.

00:52:57.750 --> 00:53:02.083
Or, if they find out you are something in life, they change.

00:53:02.417 --> 00:53:05.500
Shri Krishna was just the other way round.

00:53:05.999 --> 00:53:12.750
In His lifetime, He was always a guest of Vidhura

00:53:13.083 --> 00:53:20.458
who was the son of a Dhasi, is the servant.

00:53:20.458 --> 00:53:24.667
Maidservant's son was Vidhura, but he was a realized soul.

00:53:25.083 --> 00:53:28.208
So He used to go to his house,

00:53:28.625 --> 00:53:32.166
stay in his house, a very humble abode, Vidhura's,

00:53:32.542 --> 00:53:36.208
and eat food there, very simple food.

00:53:36.625 --> 00:53:40.500
But He would not go to the palace of Duryodhana.

00:53:42.208 --> 00:53:44.166
The other way round.

00:53:44.625 --> 00:53:47.291
I mean, somebody thinks that you have a palace,

00:53:47.625 --> 00:53:50.750
they'll be extremely kind to you, very nice, you know.

00:53:51.417 --> 00:53:54.542
But they say he lives in a hut, then he's nothing.

00:53:56.750 --> 00:53:59.542
It's such a money orientation in subtle way.

00:54:00.750 --> 00:54:03.917
Shri Krishna never, never cared for money

00:54:04.417 --> 00:54:06.750
and never bothered about it.

00:54:07.625 --> 00:54:10.083
You can see His case

00:54:10.750 --> 00:54:15.750
in which He has shown complete detachment

00:54:16.083 --> 00:54:20.208
about His throne, or His kingdom,

00:54:20.750 --> 00:54:23.667
or money part of it.

00:54:24.333 --> 00:54:28.500
Once you are attached you have all the pangs of money.

